2. UPDATE INFORMATION
This updated advisory is a follow-up to the original advisory titled ICSA-16-061-02 Rockwell Automation Allen-Bradley CompactLogix Reflective Cross-Site Scripting Vulnerability that was published March 1, 2016, on the NCCIC/ICS-CERT website. 
3. RISK EVALUATION
Successful exploitation of this vulnerability could allow an attacker to inject arbitrary JavaScript into a user’s web browser.
